416
00:29:42,920 --> 00:29:46,280
<i>If we had second chances in life,</i>
<i>I'd hope they'd choose differently</i>

417
00:29:46,360 --> 00:29:48,440
<i>but, er, sadly we don't.</i>

418
00:29:48,640 --> 00:29:51,320
