419
00:29:51,400 --> 00:29:54,080
-[woman] <i>So your verdict?</i>
<i>-Two and a half stars out of five.</i>

420
00:29:54,160 --> 00:29:55,360
<i>Disappointing.</i>

421
00:29:55,440 --> 00:29:57,520
