by slipping out one side of the maze,

2942
04:13:12,440 --> 04:13:14,600
what happens?
He comes right back in the other side.

2943
04:13:15,200 --> 04:13:16,480
People think it's a happy game,

2944
04:13:16,720 --> 04:13:19,520
